odio-api (0.4.0) trixie; urgency=high

  [ Major security and usability improvements ]
  * systemd: enforce strict permission validation on mutating operations;
    introduce safe handler patterns and comprehensive tests to mitigate
    privilege escalation risks
  * Introduce zeroconf (Avahi/mDNS) support for automatic discovery of the API
    on local networks odio-api.local:8018
  * Change default listen port to 8018 to avoid privileged port issues and reduce conflict and
    accidental exposure risks.
  * Add new command-line flags: --config <path> and --version
  * Correctly handle and report systemd configuration errors
  * Disable systemd integration by default (must now be explicitly enabled in config)


 -- Mathieu Réquillart <mathieu.requillart@gmail.com>  Fri, 13 Feb 2026 15:00:00 +0000


